To earn this deed, you must discover the entrance to the Depths of Kidzul-kâlah

You have discovered the entrance to Kidzul-kâlah. It was once a thriving mining colony of Khazad-dûm, but earthquakes and flooding led to its downfall. Now, it is said, a corrupting evil has taken root deep within.
